init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They came up with a plan to prevent any further alien invasion.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They would use the power of mana to create a force field that would prevent any alien from entering earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The council was able to convince the concerned citizens that the two child limit was in the best interest of all.
